sources.title: Shocker Internet Drive In Week 1
sources.description: Shocker Internet Drive In Week One: Relive those great old days of going to the local drive in to eat, make-out in the back seat and watch some of the most forgetable movies ever. This week we bring you Prehistoric Women and Mesa of Lost Women. Movie Website: http://shockerdrivein.dx.am or http://shockerdrivein.freeoda.com Facebook Address:  https://www.facebook.com/shockerdrivein.dx.am

metadata.Plot: Insight into the first casting organised by Reene Weston for models to be part of the Fashion Week (Gibraltar) event in April 2012. The casting was held in Puerto Banus (Marbella) on the 24th March 2012.
